data.title: The New Jersey Historical Society
data.text:
Archives: Browse Family

Family Name Files at the New Jersey Historical Society

NJHS members and patrons have donated a variety of family records over the years that the library has organized alphabetically.The following is a list of the folders on families in the collections of the library. Many names are cross-referenced, but users should also look for alternate spellings of names of interest [i.e. McGuire, MacGuire, McGwire, etc.]. An asterisk [*] indicates that there is a corresponding Bible Record for that family.
